     * obsolete, - user not found
     *
     * Throws InvalidDateParamException if: - dateRangeParam is in wrong format,
     * - date range is over MAX_STATS_DAYS
     *
     * @param projectSlug
     *            project identifier
     * @param versionSlug
     *            version identifier
     * @param username
